If you are returning to England, Wales, Scotland or Northern Ireland from Uruguay you do not need to self-isolate on your return unless you have transited a non-travel corridor country. Check the latest guidance for England, Northern Ireland, Scotland and Wales to ensure any transit country is also included in the travel corridor.
